title: Type d’espèce
text:
library(leaflet)
library(magrittr)


m <- leaflet() %>%
    addTiles() %>%  # Add default OpenStreetMap map tiles
    addMarkers(lng=45.17146, lat=-12.71570, popup="The birthplace of R")
m  # Print the map
